---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="CV – Mats Kjoshagen" description="Curriculum Vitae for Mats Kjoshagen – erfaring, utdanning og tekniske ferdigheter.">
	<style>
		/* Print styles */
		@media print {
			.print-hide { display: none !important; }
			.cv-header { padding-bottom: 1em; }
			.cv-section { break-inside: avoid; }
			body { font-size: 12pt; }
		}

		.cv-header {
			padding-bottom: 2em;
			border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
			margin-bottom: 2.5em;
			display: flex;
			justify-content: space-between;
			align-items: flex-start;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
			gap: 1.5em;
		}
		.cv-name {
			font-size: 2.25rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			color: rgb(var(--black));
			margin: 0 0 0.2em;
			background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(var(--black)) 30%, var(--accent));
			-webkit-background-clip: text;
			-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
			background-clip: text;
		}
		.cv-title {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			color: rgb(var(--gray));
			margin: 0;
		}
		.cv-contact {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 0.4em;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
			text-align: right;
		}
		.cv-contact a {
			color: var(--accent);
			text-decoration: none;
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 0.4em;
			justify-content: flex-end;
		}
		.cv-contact a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

		/* Section */
		.cv-section {
			margin-bottom: 2.5em;
		}
		.cv-section-title {
			font-size: 0.75rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			letter-spacing: 0.1em;
			color: var(--accent);
			border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
			padding-bottom: 0.4em;
			margin-bottom: 1.25em;
		}

		/* Timeline */
		.timeline {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 1.5em;
		}
		.timeline-item {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
			gap: 0 1.5em;
			padding-bottom: 1.5em;
			border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
		}
		.timeline-item:last-child {
			border-bottom: none;
			padding-bottom: 0;
		}
		.timeline-org {
			font-weight: 700;
			font-size: 1rem;
			color: rgb(var(--black));
			margin: 0 0 0.1em;
		}
		.timeline-role {
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			color: rgb(var(--gray));
			margin: 0 0 0.5em;
		}
		.timeline-desc {
			font-size: 0.9rem;
			color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
			margin: 0;
			line-height: 1.6;
		}
		.timeline-desc ul {
			margin: 0.4em 0 0;
			padding-left: 1.25em;
		}
		.timeline-desc li {
			margin-bottom: 0.25em;
		}
		.timeline-period {
			font-size: 0.8rem;
			color: rgb(var(--gray));
			white-space: nowrap;
			background: rgb(var(--surface));
			border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
			border-radius: 100px;
			padding: 0.2em 0.8em;
			height: fit-content;
			font-weight: 600;
		}

		/* Skills */
		.skills-categories {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
			gap: 1.25em;
		}
		.skill-category h4 {
			font-size: 0.85rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			letter-spacing: 0.06em;
			color: rgb(var(--gray));
			margin: 0 0 0.6em;
		}
		.skill-pills {
			display: flex;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
			gap: 0.4em;
		}
		.skill-pill {
			background: rgb(var(--surface));
			border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
			border-radius: 100px;
			padding: 0.25em 0.75em;
			font-size: 0.8rem;
			color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
			font-weight: 600;
		}

		/* Languages */
		.lang-list {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 0.75em;
		}
		.lang-item {
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: space-between;
		}
		.lang-name {
			font-weight: 600;
			color: rgb(var(--black));
			font-size: 0.95rem;
		}
		.lang-level {
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 0.5em;
		}
		.lang-dots {
			display: flex;
			gap: 4px;
		}
		.lang-dot {
			width: 10px;
			height: 10px;
			border-radius: 50%;
			background: rgb(var(--gray-light));
		}
		.lang-dot.filled {
			background: var(--accent);
		}
		.lang-label {
			font-size: 0.8rem;
			color: rgb(var(--gray));
		}

		/* Print button */
		.print-btn {
			margin-bottom: 2em;
			display: flex;
			justify-content: flex-end;
		}
		.print-btn button {
			background: transparent;
			border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
			border-radius: 6px;
			padding: 0.4em 1em;
			font-size: 0.85rem;
			cursor: pointer;
			color: rgb(var(--gray));
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 0.4em;
			transition: background var(--transition), color var(--transition);
		}
		.print-btn button:hover {
			background: rgb(var(--surface));
			color: rgb(var(--black));
		}

		@media (max-width: 560px) {
			.cv-header { flex-direction: column; }
			.cv-contact { text-align: left; }
			.cv-contact a { justify-content: flex-start; }
			.timeline-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
			.timeline-period { width: fit-content; }
		}
	</style>

	<div class="print-btn print-hide">
		<button onclick="window.print()">🖨️ Skriv ut / Lagre som PDF</button>
	</div>

	<header class="cv-header">
		<div>
			<h1 class="cv-name">Mats Kjoshagen</h1>
			<p class="cv-title">IT-utvikler · Fullstack · Skyinfrastruktur</p>
		</div>
		<address class="cv-contact">
			<a href="mailto:mats@kjoshagen.online">📧 mats@kjoshagen.online</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/matskkolstad" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">🐙 github.com/matskkolstad</a>
			<a href="https://kjoshagen.online">🌐 kjoshagen.online</a>
			<span style="color:rgb(var(--gray));font-size:0.85rem">📍 Norge</span>
		</address>
	</header>

	<!-- Summary -->
	<section class="cv-section">
		<h2 class="cv-section-title">Sammendrag</h2>
		<p>
			Engasjert IT-utvikler med erfaring innen fullstack-utvikling, skyinfrastruktur og
			automatisering. Jeg er opptatt av kodekvalitet, gode utviklingspraksiser og å levere
			robuste løsninger. Jeg søker en stilling der jeg kan vokse faglig, bidra i et sterkt team
			og jobbe med teknologi jeg brenner for.
		</p>
	</section>

	<!-- Experience -->
	<section class="cv-section">
		<h2 class="cv-section-title">Arbeidserfaring</h2>
		<div class="timeline">
			<div class="timeline-item">
				<div>
					<p class="timeline-org">Din nåværende arbeidsgiver</p>
					<p class="timeline-role">IT-utvikler</p>
					<div class="timeline-desc">
						<ul>
							<li>Utviklet og vedlikeholdt fullstack-webapplikasjoner</li>
							<li>Jobbet med CI/CD-pipelines og skyinfrastruktur</li>
							<li>Bidrog til forbedring av kodebasen og interne utviklingsprosesser</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<span class="timeline-period">20XX – nå</span>
			</div>

			<div class="timeline-item">
				<div>
					<p class="timeline-org">Tidligere arbeidsgiver / internship</p>
					<p class="timeline-role">Utvikler / Intern</p>
					<div class="timeline-desc">
						<ul>
							<li>Bidrog til utvikling av interne systemer og verktøy</li>
							<li>Erfaring med agile arbeidsmetoder og tverrfaglig samarbeid</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<span class="timeline-period">20XX – 20XX</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Education -->
	<section class="cv-section">
		<h2 class="cv-section-title">Utdanning</h2>
		<div class="timeline">
			<div class="timeline-item">
				<div>
					<p class="timeline-org">Din høyskole / universitet</p>
					<p class="timeline-role">Bachelor i informatikk / IT</p>
					<p class="timeline-desc">Spesialisering innen [f.eks. programvareutvikling, nettverk, datasikkerhet].</p>
				</div>
				<span class="timeline-period">20XX – 20XX</span>
			</div>

			<div class="timeline-item">
				<div>
					<p class="timeline-org">Videregående skole</p>
					<p class="timeline-role">Studiespesialisering</p>
				</div>
				<span class="timeline-period">20XX – 20XX</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Skills -->
	<section class="cv-section">
		<h2 class="cv-section-title">Tekniske ferdigheter</h2>
		<div class="skills-categories">
			<div class="skill-category">
				<h4>Frontend</h4>
				<div class="skill-pills">
					<span class="skill-pill">TypeScript</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">JavaScript</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">React</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">Astro</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">HTML / CSS</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="skill-category">
				<h4>Backend</h4>
				<div class="skill-pills">
					<span class="skill-pill">Node.js</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">Python</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">REST API</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">SQL</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">PostgreSQL</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="skill-category">
				<h4>Infrastruktur & DevOps</h4>
				<div class="skill-pills">
					<span class="skill-pill">Docker</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">Linux</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">Git</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">Cloudflare</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">Azure</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">CI/CD</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="skill-category">
				<h4>Verktøy</h4>
				<div class="skill-pills">
					<span class="skill-pill">VS Code</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">GitHub</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">Jira</span>
					<span class="skill-pill">Figma</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Languages -->
	<section class="cv-section">
		<h2 class="cv-section-title">Språk</h2>
		<div class="lang-list">
			<div class="lang-item">
				<span class="lang-name">Norsk</span>
				<div class="lang-level">
					<div class="lang-dots">
						<div class="lang-dot filled"></div>
						<div class="lang-dot filled"></div>
						<div class="lang-dot filled"></div>
						<div class="lang-dot filled"></div>
						<div class="lang-dot filled"></div>
					</div>
					<span class="lang-label">Morsmål</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="lang-item">
				<span class="lang-name">Engelsk</span>
				<div class="lang-level">
					<div class="lang-dots">
						<div class="lang-dot filled"></div>
						<div class="lang-dot filled"></div>
						<div class="lang-dot filled"></div>
						<div class="lang-dot filled"></div>
						<div class="lang-dot"></div>
					</div>
					<span class="lang-label">Meget god</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
